The folder prune_layers_All uses SLP normalization parameters based upon the MNIST dataset.
This gives better (lower) CE and higher IPA and  therefore we should use this.
Whereas:
The folder prune_layers_ALL_Normalize-0.5 uses 0.5 as normalization parameters.
This version gives higher CE at the same stop criteria (delta CE < .01) and overall
lower IPA and therefore we do not use this normalization scheme.

